column4:
Search for the reaction $e^{+}e^{-} \rightarrow \pi ^{+}\pi ^{-}
  \chi_{cJ}$ and a charmonium-like structure decaying to $\chi_{cJ}\pi ^{\pm}$
  between 4.18 and 4.60 GeV

column5:
16 pages, 7 figures. Key Words: Plasticity; Action potential; Timing;
  Error redaction; Synchronization; Quantum phase computation; Phase ternary
  computation; Retinal model
